### 1. User Signup
POST {{baseUrl}}/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

### 2. User Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "securePassword123"
}

### 3. Refresh Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}

### 4. Get User Profile (Protected Route - Placeholder)
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE}}

